data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Step into this well maintained 3BR, 2BA, 1,392 sqft West Salem home. The kitchen is a culinary dream with slab granite, Samsung appliances, and a stone backsplash. Cozy up by the wood-burning fireplace, and relish in two living areas and a versatile loft space. Updates include electrical, updated baths, backyard French drain, and an instant hot water system. Located in a desirable West Salem location, this home is a perfect blend of classic allure and contemporary comfort. Act fast—your dream home awaits!
